    • build

      public final Alert build()
      Builds the alert from the specified data.

      The alert URI defaults to the one from the HistoryReference or HttpMessage if set.

      Note: If the Alert has a CWE set then an associated Tag will be added during build()

      Returns:
      the alert with specified data.
